      "text": "<blockquote><ul><li>Traditional media puts things in a sterile, manageable place. Here are dead children. A crush of people. Btw, don’t you want a bigger car?\n<li>Even when they tell you, they tell you in a way that distances you. The anchor & the correspondent are distant, so you remain distant.\n<li>On the other hand, there are billions of people & many tragedies. Not possible to live w/ it all, all the time. No answers, just reflecting.</blockquote>\n\n"
